source.name: NOAA's Southeast and Caribbean Data Explorer Geoportal
source.description: The Southeast and Caribbean Data Explorer provides public access to NOAA geospatial data within the land areas of North Carolina, South Carolina, Georgia, Florida, Puerto Rico, and the US Virgin Islands, and the marine environment directly adjacent to these lands. This one-stop shop for NOAA geospatial data within the region can be searched by keyword, topic, or location.
